params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The request project that owns the session, in the form of projects/{project_id}.

params.name: data.max_stream_count
params.description: Max initial number of streams. If unset or zero, the server will provide a value of streams so as to produce reasonable throughput. Must be non-negative. The number of streams may be lower than the requested number, depending on the amount parallelism that is reasonable for the table. Error will be returned if the max count is greater than the current system max limit of 1,000. Streams must be read starting from offset 0.
